KPatcher
========

This product includes or ports code from the following:

  DeNCS (KotOR NCS → NSS decompiler; also referred to historically as NCSDecomp)
  - Upstream: https://github.com/OldRepublicDevs/DeNCS
  - Vendored reference: vendor/DeNCS/
  - Copyright (c) 2021-2025 DeNCS contributors
  - Licensed under the MIT License (see licenses/DeNCS-MIT.txt and file-level headers in ported sources).

Original DeNCS developers: JdNoa (Script Decompiler), Dashus (GUI).
Current maintainer: OldRepublicDevs (https://openkotor.com).

The C# projects NCSDecomp.Core, NCSDecomp.NET, and NCSDecomp.UI are managed ports
of that codebase for KPatcher; DeNCS-derived portions use the same MIT terms.
